{"tid":501914,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"Roselia今井リサ 聲優遠藤ゆりか5月末引退","createTime":"2017-12-17T11:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T14:48:56.000Z","uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cc2e6c9c54fb10035ef086406b3de1d5193f938c","tid":501914,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:02:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Megxa.hk/posts/1490682134360463\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FMegxa.hk%2Fposts%2F1490682134360463&d=rgQ2oB%2B6oMbIQfighRH3gv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=72487cd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Megxa.hk/posts/1490682134360463</a><br />\n聲優遠藤ゆりか經事務所網站宣布會從明年5月完結起從聲優、歌手等一切藝能工作中引退，至今公布過會出席的活動不會取消，而且會在引退前舉行solo live。<br />\n<br />\n引退聲明中，遠藤提及自己從5年前試鏡合格起，在成為聲優和歌手的道路上獲得了很多不同的經驗。但身體狀況實在追不上工作環境的變化，身體不適的情況也不斷發生，不能全力以赴去聲演角色對她來說非常苦惱，為了能繼續能在未來的人生往前走，於是最後做了引退的決定。她也對不能負責自己擔當的角色和作品到最後感到抱歉。<br />\n<br />\n事務所官網聲明：<a href=\"https://t.co/5mb97rCXhK?amp=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F5mb97rCXhK%3Famp%3D1&d=rgQ2oB%2B6oMbIQfighRH3gv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4b98d25a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/5mb97rCXhK?amp=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/C7xvo_rVMAA9lDr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FC7xvo_rVMAA9lDr.jpg&h=9001eacc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b79dc51b85194b56d275bc4e95345828df2bf8c","tid":501914,"uid":129739,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:05:16.000Z","msg":"都係你地班聲豚"},{"pid":"04d3d01b3140b46e4baca3f00c44cc03b08cb04a","tid":501914,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:12:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/191107_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F20